{"tid":473277,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"公民黨梁家傑：國安法大致框架已存在","createTime":"2017-11-19T05:40:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-19T05:46:21.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"91e5d24638a63a6f4339e6595cc0b00a11aa3898","tid":473277,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T05:40:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1365657-20171119.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1365657-20171119.htm&d=xUcJZgEr%2B061WxnRHYnldMP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=2db4ed48\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1365657-20171119.htm&h=faa8123e\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1365657-20171119.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n基本法委員會主任李飛日前說，基本法23條未立法，不良影響有目共睹，香港在維護國家主權和安全，責無旁貸。<br />\n<br />\n公民黨主席梁家傑在本台節目《城市論壇》說，23條涉及的7宗罪，在刑事罪行條例、社團條例和公安條例等已有規管，國安法大致框架已經存在，不同意李飛所講在法律上有缺位。<br />\n<br />\n教協副會長張銳輝說，若要犧牲香港利益完成立法，一定會撕裂社會。<br />\n<br />\n港區全國人大代表葉國謙說，不同意23條立法參考《國歌法》，以附件三形式列入基本法，因為23條是特區政府自行立法的憲制責任。<br />\n<br />\n基本法推廣督導委員會委員劉炳章就說，不同意以斬件式或梅花間竹式立法，即先處理威脅國家安全的法例，然後處理政改，之後再就23條其他部分立法，他認為爭議只會更多、拖延更長時間。"},{"pid":"c79b46494c249fb38b7b5629d74de8a6a1343c33","tid":473277,"uid":22858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T05:46:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>公安條例已經嚴到仆街啦</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZgXLysvzBv8/UJpcUjLy6uI/AAAAAAAAAcs/_KN4eCwYtos/s1600/hkflagIl759.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ZgXLysvzBv8%2FUJpcUjLy6uI%2FAAAAAAAAAcs%2F_KN4eCwYtos%2Fs1600%2FhkflagIl759.gif&h=88ac342b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZgXLysvzBv8/UJpcUjLy6uI/AAAAAAAAAcs/_KN4eCwYtos/s1600/hkflagIl759.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ZgXLysv